### Admin login
POST http://localhost:5000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email" : "admin@mail.com",
    "password" : "admin"
}


### Read all users and authors (email)
GET http://localhost:5000/admin-api/all


### Block or Activate users or authors (email)
PATCH http://localhost:5000/admin-api/all
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email":"user1@mail.com",
    "isActive":false 
}
